title: Facebook to allow users to message across different apps
text: CNBC's Julia Boorstin reports on Facebook CEO Mark Zuckerberg's announcement the company will integrate messengers on social media.

title: Teen takes on Facebook over spread of vaccination myths
text: Dr. Mikhail Varshavski and Ethan Lindenberger, who got vaccinated against his mother's wishes, discuss concerns over the spread of misinformation on health-care issues such as vaccinations.
